      "span_text": "This is consistent with the report of that observed no mortality of earthworms on the bioremediation of pyrene with E. foetida, but contrasted that of ContrerasRamos et al. (2006) with 80 % survival of E. foetida in soil amended with anthracene and benzo(a)pyrene."
